OL,3,CCouple beat odds as both called to
OL,4,Cdonate stem cells
OL,6,FWatch Antoine Allen's report.
OL,8,FA married couple from London and NHS
OL,9,FBlood and Transplant (NHSBT) are now
OL,10,Fcalling on people of Asian heritage to
OL,11,Fbecome stem cell donors.
OL,13,FNirav and Kanan Chokshi were called
OL,14,Fseparately to donate stem cells to
OL,15,Fadult leukaemia patients in need of
OL,16,Fpotentially life-saving transplants.
OL,18,FMr Chokshi signed up to become a stem
OL,19,Fcell donor in 2016 and donated in
OL,20,F2018. After seeing his experience, his
OL,21,Fwife signed up and donated in 2024.
