OL,3,CCouple beat odds as both called to
OL,4,Cdonate stem cells
OL,6,FAgainst the odds, the pair have
OL,7,Fmanaged to offer a lifeline to two
OL,8,Fdifferent cancer patients.
OL,10,FMrs Chokshi, a 44-year-old school
OL,11,Flunchtime supervisor, told ITV News:
OL,12,F"I feel proud and blessed that we did
OL,13,Fthat and we saved someone's life."
OL,15,FNirav and Kanan Chokshi were born in
OL,16,FIndia but now live in Hounslow, west
OL,17,FLondon with their two children,
OL,18,FShiven, 15, and Siya, 11.
OL,20,FWhat's involved in donating blood stem
OL,21,Fcells?
