OL,3,CCouple beat odds as both called to
OL,4,Cdonate stem cells
OL,6,FPeople signed up to the NHS Stem Cell
OL,7,FDonor Registry have a one in 2,000
OL,8,Fchance of being called to donate.
OL,10,FNHS Blood and Transplant (NHSBT) said
OL,11,Fthere was a one in four million chance
OL,12,Fthat a married couple would both be
OL,13,Fcalled up to donate.
OL,15,FNHSBT said it can be significantly
OL,16,Fmore difficult to find a suitable
OL,17,Fmatch for patients of Asian, black and
OL,18,Fmixed ethnicity backgrounds due to the
OL,19,Flack of suitable potential donors on
OL,20,Fthe register.
