OL,3,CCouple beat odds as both called to
OL,4,Cdonate stem cells
OL,6,FMr Chokshi, a mechanical engineer,
OL,7,Ftold ITV News: "There are more chances
OL,8,Fof someone within your own community
OL,9,Fto match with you. I would encourage
OL,10,Feveryone to come forward (to donate
OL,11,Ftheir stem cells)."
OL,13,FGuy Parkes, head of stem cell donation
OL,14,Fand transplantation at NHSBT, said:
OL,15,F"In order to find the perfect,
OL,16,Fpotentially lifesaving transplant for
OL,17,Fas many people as possible, we need
OL,18,Fmore people of Asian or black heritage
OL,19,Fand from mixed ethnic backgrounds to
OL,20,Fjoin the register ` your stem cells
OL,21,Fcould help save a life."
